(1699, 1, '2017-06-20 18:37:04', '2017-06-20 18:37:04', 'The \'Rawcliffe\' name has been associated with valuation practice ownership within Hawke\'s Bay for a continued period over 40 years.\r\n\r\nFollowing a lengthy 26 year partnership, Terry Rawcliffe preferred to operate as an independent specialised practice providing advisory, valuation and commercial management services by forming the company now known as Rawcliffe &amp; Co.\r\nCompany policy recognises professional valuation/consultancy services regularly influences important negotiations and property dealings. Therefore the provision of well researched innovative solutions to clients remains of the utmost priority.\r\nIn this responsibility, Rawcliffe &amp; Co strive to ensure all valuations and professional services are carefully undertaken without conflict, by experienced and independent Registered Valuers, who are conversant with all market and influencing factors.\r\n\r\nRawcliffe &amp; Co rely upon a wide and varied support network, including trusted professional advisors, other specialised consultants the likes of Engineers, Registered Surveyors, Plant and Machinery Valuers, to ensure client expectations are appropriately dealt with.\r\n\r\nThrough experience and commitment to quality and service, Rawcliffe &amp; Co are highly respected by a wide and diverse base of clients, with an inhouse resource of 11,000 property records.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-06-20 18:37:04', '2017-06-20 18:37:04', '', 0, 'http://wordpress.dev/?page_id=1699', 0, 'page', '', 0),
